These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
House: futuristic, craftsman
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| House   | futuristic | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: radish, carrot
1. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Food   | radish | carrot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia
1. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Flower   | dahlia | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |
| Transport   | motorbike | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-5::.
